{"tid":874173,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無邊套戲你每次睇返都會令你諗起一個人","createTime":"2018-10-24T04:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T04:32:31.000Z","uid":18468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ef1ca0d319db1f4e3ce788ccb57cf5feaa06dc32","tid":874173,"uid":18468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i3V6666.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi3V6666.jpg&h=a57b2a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然呢套戲整體唔算好高水平<br />\n不過有時有D戲 坐係隔離陪你睇既果個人會令到套戲加分好多<br />\n記得當時睇完套戲<br />\n你問我「如果我有日消失左，你會唔會好似男主角咁樣搵我？」<br />\n我當時好傻咁答你「我唔會比你離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n當然呢個網絡發達既年代 一個人好難完全消失<br />\n不過都再無勇氣去SD出果個MSG 打果個電話<br />\n雖然我地經歷左好多野 但最尾都無一齊到<br />\n你都已經有自己既生活 有自己既另一半<br />\n不過我仍然每日都有諗起你 無停過<br />\n王家欣，你喺邊度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469ef13ab17925d276839b8d9ad1e40fe4fe4336","tid":874173,"uid":122134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:25:02.000Z","msg":"戲就少<br />\n歌先多 有D歌係某段時間狂聽<br />\n過左一排無聽  再聽返 <br />\n就好似返返去個時咁...<br />\n所以事/人都湧返出黎"},{"pid":"2d5a3ea4a46db5665b882fe8e0eb22e249861a8e","tid":874173,"uid":207099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"469ef13ab17925d276839b8d9ad1e40fe4fe4336","tid":874173,"uid":122134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:25:02.000Z","msg":"戲就少<br />\n歌先多 有D歌係某段時間狂聽<br />\n過左一排無聽  再聽返 <br />\n就好似返返去個時咁...<br />\n所以事/人都湧返出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:30:33.000Z","msg":"呢句講得啱 我果首係 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IukpM1Lw0x0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIukpM1Lw0x0&d=gdSRabkEe1ynn%2FDb2mZ3o7IOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f10e6997\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IukpM1Lw0x0</a>"},{"pid":"d3af525329b6df0049b45b3533e679403cf47880","tid":874173,"uid":18468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":